{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a48192d9-64cc-4dd0-a9ed-8ea6b5c2a180","content":"The workspace is empty — this is a general guidance question. Here's what you need to know:\n\n---\n\n### Evaluation file format\n\nCreate an `evaluation.yml` at the root of your skill plugin. It's a YAML file with a list of evaluation scenarios:\n\n```yaml\n- question: \"What's the cheapest laptop in the catalog?\"\n  expected_tool_calls:\n    - tool: search_products\n      parameters:\n        category: \"laptops\"\n        sort_by: \"price_asc\"\n  expected_response_contains:\n    - \"laptop\"\n    - price pattern or product name\n```\n\nEach entry has a **question** (the user prompt), **expected tool calls** (which tools the LLM should invoke and with what parameters), and **expected response** assertions.\n\n---\n\n### What makes a good evaluation question\n\n1. **Direct tool use** — \"List all products in the 'Audio' category.\" Tests basic tool invocation with correct parameters.\n\n2. **Multi-tool chaining** — \"Compare the prices of product A and product B.\" Forces the LLM to call a tool multiple times and synthesize results.\n\n3. **Parameter extraction** — \"Find wireless headphones under $50.\" Tests whether the LLM correctly maps natural language filters to tool parameters (category, max price, features).\n\n4. **Ambiguity handling** — \"What's the best product?\" Tests whether the LLM asks for clarification or makes a reasonable tool call.\n\n5. **No-tool-needed** — \"What does this catalog tool do?\" Ensures the LLM doesn't hallucinate tool calls when none are needed.\n\n6. **Edge cases** — \"Find products in the 'Spaceship' category.\" Tests graceful handling of empty results.\n\n**Tips:**\n- Cover each tool at least once individually\n- Include at least one multi-step scenario\n- Vary phrasing — don't always mirror the tool's parameter names\n- Test that the LLM uses the **right** tool, not just **a** tool\n\nWant me to scaffold an `evaluation.yml` for your specific catalog tools?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c67a484b-7825-4c0b-8fda-7ab187e89db5","outputTokens":477,"requestId":"CC24:BAB4E:B9D376:D7D7E9:69EAC09F"},"id":"be518235-8411-4518-bae9-9a2cc3ec8d90","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:00:27.995Z","parentId":"a00ecf67-78f4-496e-a49a-4dba6bba3155"}
